We’ve got four: 

🍫 A perfect chocolate coating for @Magnum 

🌍Reduced carbon emissions from our factories 

♻ Flexible, recyclable packaging for sachets 

🏭 And a fully operational factory in a box the size of a shipping container 

Watch this IGTV video to find out more about the women engineers who brought these ideas to life.
